\c 3
\s Yambiro yaPauro pamusoro pekururama kwevanhu
\p
\v 1 Pakupedzisira, hama dzangu, farai muna Ishe. Kukunyorerai zvinhu zvimwechetezvo, kwandiri zvirokwazvo hazvinetesi, asi kwamuri zvinokusimbisai.
\p
\v 2 Chenjererai imbwa, chenjererai vabati vakaipa, chenjererai vekucheka;
\v 3 nokuti isu tiri kudzingiswa, vanonamata Mwari muMweya, tichizvirumbidza muna Kristu Jesu, uye tisingavimbi nenyama;
\v 4 kunyange ini ndingavawo nechivimbo munyama; kana umwewo achifunga kuvimba nenyama, zvikuru ini;
\v 5 ndakadzingiswa nezuva rerusere, \add ndiri\add* werudzi rwaIsraeri, \add we\add*rudzi rwaBhenjamini, muHebheru weVaHebheru; zviri zvemurairo \add ndiri\add* muFarisi;
\v 6 maererano nekushingaira ndichishusha kereke; maererano nekururama kuri mumurairo ndisina chandingapomerwa.
\p
\v 7 Asi zvinhu zvaiva mubairo kwandiri, ndizvo zvandakaverenga kuva kurasikirwa nekuda kwaKristu.
\v 8 Hongu zvirokwazvo, uye ndinoverenga zvinhu zvose kuva kurasikirwa nekuda kwekunakisisa kweruzivo rwaKristu Jesu Ishe wangu, wandakarasikirwa nezvinhu zvose nekuda kwake, ndikazviidza kuva marara, kuti ndiwane Kristu;
\v 9 uye ndiwanikwe maari, ndisina kururama kwangu kunobva kumurairo, asi kunobudikidzwa nerutendo rwaKristu, kururama kunobva kuna Mwari nerutendo;
\v 10 kuti ndimuzive iye, nesimba rekumuka kwake, nekudyidzana kwematambudziko ake, nditodze kufa kwake,
\v 11 kana zvingagoneka ndisvike pakumuka kwevakafa.
\p
\v 12 Handi\add revi\add* kuti ndakato\add chi\add*wana, kana ndakatokwaniswa, asi ndinoteverera, kuti ndichibatewo, chandakabatirwawo naKristu Jesu.
\v 13 Hama, ini handizviverengi kuti ndachibata, asi \add ndinoita\add* chinhu chimwe, ndichikanganwa zvinhu zviri shure, ndichinanavira zvinhu zviri mberi,
\v 14 ndinoteverera kuchinangwa, kumubairo wekudana kwekumusoro kwaMwari muna Kristu Jesu.
\v 15 Naizvozvo isu tese takakwana, ngative nemufungo uyu; uye kana zvimwe mune umwe mufungo, Mwari achakuratidzai kunyange izvi.
\v 16 Asi pane patasvika, ngatifambe nemurairo iwoyu tifunge chinhu ichochi.
\v 17 Hama, ivai vatevedzeri vangu pamwe, natsai kutarira avo vanofamba saizvozvo sezvamakava nesu semuenzaniso.
\v 18 Nokuti vazhinji vanofamba, vandakakuudzai nezvavo kazhinji, nazvino ndinokuudzai kunyange nekuchema, vavengi vemuchinjikwa waKristu;
\v 19 kuguma kwavo kuparadzwa, mwari wavo \add i\add*dumbu \add ravo\add*, uye kurumbidzwa \add kuri\add* mukunyadzwa kwavo, vanofunga zvenyika.
\v 20 Nokuti ubwo hwedu huri kumatenga, uko kwatakataririrawo kuti Muponesi achabva, Ishe Jesu Kristu;
\v 21 uyo achavandudza muviri wekuninipiswa kwedu, kuti ufananidzwe nemuviri wekubwinya kwake, nesimba iro raanogonawo naro kuisa zvinhu zvose pasi pake.
